Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:16.51,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正大标宋_GBK\b1\fs22\fad(200,200)}\N不如随波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.59,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正大标宋_GBK\b1\fs22\fad(200,200)}\N产生于误会的梦想
